snippet.title: M64 MKDD Extended v2 - The BIGGEST Double Dash ModPack! (32 NEW Custom Tracks)
snippet.description:
I showcase M64 MKDD Extended, a Brand New Mario Kart: Double Dash ModPack that features 32 Custom Tracks, 2 New Battle Arenas, New Vehicles & even a 200cc Gamemode. #mariokart #mariokartdoubledash #boostercoursepass 

This is just a PREVIEW of V2. You can check out V1 here:
https://youtu.be/bsai91whCqs?si=I0zQTAQpvAw7H3eU

Credits: 
This project was made by:  @M64-Snyderz64  

Custom Tracks/Vehicles are made by The Double Dash Modding Community. 

** All music is In-Game. Some BRSTMs are Remixes that I don't entirely know who made them, but the track creators individually got permission for them (as far as I know.) **

Full Track List:

3DS Toad circuit - ExxitZero
DS Cheep Cheep Beach - Majas de pic
Wii Coconut Mall - King Boo Gaming
DS Desert Hill - Majas de pic
GBA Luigi Circuit - ExxitZero
N64 Mario Circuit - Bruh de la Boi
Wii Daisy Circuit - Yosh Fr
DS Wario Stadium - Majas de pic
Wii DK Summit - Vodquik
GBA Peach Circuit - tarsa129
DS Delfino Square - Yosh Fr
N64 DK Jungle Parkway - Geras
Wii Luigi Circuit - Atlas
N64 Kalimari desert - ExxitZero
Wii Moonview Highway - King Boo Gaming
SNES Rainbow Road - PiPPiN
3DS Mario Circuit - ExxitZero
GBA Shy Guy Beach - Cherry
DS Shroom Ridge - Casini Loogi
3DS Shy Guy Bazaar - ExxitZero
DS Airship Fortress - unknown, and M64
N64 Toad Turnpike - King Boo Gaming
GBA Sky Garden - ExxitZero
N64 Choco Mountain - Casini Loogi
N64 Frappe Snowland - ExxitZero
DS Peach Garden - Geras
DS Mario Circuit - Majas de pic
GBA Riverside Park - ExxitZero
Wii Wario Gold Mine - cristian64
SNES Choco Island 2 - Cherry
N64 Banshee Boardwalk - ExxitZero
Rainbow Avenue - ExxitZero

Battle Arenas:

Wii Funky Stadium - Bruh de la Boi
N64 Double Deck - Retrostyle12 

0:00 Overview of Pack
0:59 Custom Track Cups 1 - 4
15:14 Custom Track Cups 5 - 8
30:04 Battle Arenas

Thank you for watching!
